tip.text: Pasta Carbonara is good but best shared with 2 persons. A bit too much for one because of the creaminess.
Mr. Benedict gets a 7/10 from me. Not really done to my liking, it feels kind of heavy.
Pocket's Benedict with Buffalo Cheese, Sun-dried tomatoes and basil oil. 😘👍👍 Available only from 10am-3.30pm though.
Belgian Cheesecake is good. 😄 lovely ambiance, cozy and comfortable.
Strawberry Cheese Moussé 👍👍 too good till forgot to take picture 😝
